ODD or EVEN

#modulo '%' is used to calculate the remainder after a division
#if the given number is divisible by 2, then it is said to be an even number
#else, it is considered as an odd number

number = int(input("Which number do you want to check? "))
if (number % 2) == 0:
  print("This is an even number.")
else:
  print("This is an odd number.")
  
o/p: Which number do you want to check? 18
     This is an even number.

     Which number do you want to check? 11
     This is an odd number.
